title: Looking for Coaches!
body:
Hello!

I am currently recruiting coaches for Ender Gaming, a community of all servers and ranks!
We are looking for experienced players, Plat + with the patience and will to help others improve!
We need you to be active and helpful in anyway possible, and ensure to spare some time to hold private coaching sessions!

If you are interested, join our server: https://discord.gg/tDBJp7u

Message @YAINT when you join!
